{"tid":1804913,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［功能界別］未申請，求教學","createTime":"2019-12-31T10:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T10:46:50.000Z","uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e15b9117dd69778348671a420f3ccf358ba310ae","tid":1804913,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"首先，希望各位識嘅手足可以提供下教學<br />\n未識嘅可以喺度問下問題，我間唔中會整合下<br />\n<br />\n入正題，前幾日選舉辦事處寄咗封信俾我，然後邀請我登記做第二功能界別嘅選民，佢話我依家係地方選區選民，但未登記任何功能界別（包括區議會（第二）功能界別）<br />\n所以邀請我登記成為區議會（第二）功能界別嘅選民<br />\n<br />\n我想問：<br />\n如果申請咗第二功能界別係咪就唔可以申請其他功能界別？<br />\n如果係將來有冇得轉界別？<br />\n同埋學生有冇其他界別可以選擇？"},{"pid":"0382d0e52d2be0d1be8a6d31208bf6d526e79110","tid":1804913,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:25:46.000Z","msg":"係咪開錯台？"},{"pid":"be8ed727c77b94ac5e4e9ee387d8c8c9d9c9f6ba","tid":1804913,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:32:50.000Z","msg":"<code>德美 聯署 整合</code><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804604</a>"},{"pid":"79b390116bbdfe53e5b336186a2635d1470ac367","tid":1804913,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be8ed727c77b94ac5e4e9ee387d8c8c9d9c9f6ba","tid":1804913,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:32:50.000Z","msg":"<code>德美 聯署 整合</code><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804604</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:44:27.000Z","msg":"Signed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d1e6f1a0c8306e39deaa615b7d2946b94600e2","tid":1804913,"uid":317979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"［最後幾個鐘］要出絕招喇 德國聯署機！全中文版！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804848\" data-au